{"type":"question","id":13190,"title":"从历朝历代宦官来看，明朝种族主义过头了？","uid":21662,"topics":[4248],"contents":"[sup]&nbsp;[/sup]<br>\n<br>\n秦朝<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Eunuch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">编辑</a><br>\n被判处<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Castration\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">ration割的</a>人们被变成了<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Qin_dynasty\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">秦朝的</a>&nbsp;un官，从事诸如<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Terracotta_Army\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">秦始皇兵马俑</a>等工程的强迫劳动。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-39\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[39]</a>秦政府没收了财产，奴役了接受cast割作为惩罚的强奸犯家庭。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-40\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[40]</a>在<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Han_dynasty\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">汉代，</a>受到cast割惩罚的人也被用作奴隶。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-41\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[41]</a><br>\n<br>\n汉代<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Eunuch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">编辑</a><br>\n在<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Han_dynasty\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">汉代，</a>&nbsp;cast割继续被用作对各种罪行的惩罚。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-42\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[42]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-43\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[43]</a>&nbsp;著名的中国历史学家<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sima_Qian\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">司马迁</a>因异议而被中国汉高祖下令cast割。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-44\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[44]</a>在另一起事件中，包括首席抄写员及其下属在内的多个人遭到cast割。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-45\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[45]</a><br>\n<br>\n唐朝<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Eunuch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">编辑</a><br>\n隋唐时期，中国南方的土著部落被用作太监。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-46\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[46]</a><br>\n<br>\n辽代<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Eunuch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">编辑</a><br>\n该<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Khitan_people\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">契丹</a>通过使用来自中国的太监的实践和太监是战争的非契丹囚犯。当他们建立<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liao_dynasty\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">辽朝时，</a>他们发展了一个由conc妃和妻子组成的<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harem\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">后宫</a>系统，并采用了太监。契丹人入侵<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Later_Jin_(Five_Dynasties)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">后来的晋国</a>时，在晋廷俘虏了中国的太监。另一个消息来源是在与<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Song_dynasty\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">宋朝</a>的战争中，契丹会袭击中国，将汉族男孩俘虏为战俘并<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emasculate\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">割</a>他们成为太监。被俘虏的中国男孩的去雄确保了在辽朝后宫中持续供应太监。皇太后承天在突袭行动中扮演了重要角色，以俘虏和污男孩。她亲自领导自己的军队在986年击败了宋军，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-47\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[47]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-48\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[48]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-49\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[49]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-50\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[50]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-51\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[51]</a>与撤退的中国军队作战。然后，她下令the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Castration\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">杀</a>大约100个被俘的中国男孩，并补充了契丹供<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Wang_Ji%27en_(Liao_Dynasty_eunuch)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">官</a>的太监，其中包括<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Wang_Ji%27en_(Liao_Dynasty_eunuch)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">王继恩</a>。这些男孩都在10岁以下，并因其外表好而被选中。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Jay-52\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[52]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-53\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[53]</a><br>\n<br>\n元朝<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Eunuch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">编辑</a><br>\n像蒙古帝国的所有地区一样，高丽为蒙古人提供了太监。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-54\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[54]</a>其中之一是Bak Bulhwa，他对高丽造成了伤害。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-55\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[55]</a><br>\n<br>\n明朝<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Eunuch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">编辑</a><br>\n有来自中国各个民族的太监，蒙古，韩国，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-56\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[56]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-SchirokauerBrown2012-57\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[57]</a>越南，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Walker2012-58\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[58]</a>柬埔寨，中亚，泰国和冲绳。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Tsai1996-59\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[59]</a>：14-16<br>\n<br>\n在<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yongle_Emperor\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">永乐皇帝统治时期</a>，有朝鲜人，女真人，蒙古人，中亚人和越南太监<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Dardess2012_2-60\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[60]</a>：36ff&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-MoteTwitchett1988-61\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[61]，</a>其中包括蒙古王太子担任蒙古太监。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Tsai2011_2-62\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[62]</a>穆斯林和蒙古太监存在于明朝，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Tsai1996-59\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[59]&nbsp;</a>：14如那些来自蒙古控制捕获<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yunnan\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">云南</a>&nbsp;1381年，以及它们之间是大明航海探险家<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zheng_He\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">郑和下西洋</a>，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Tsai1996-59\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[59]&nbsp;</a>：14FF&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-63\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[ 63]</a>。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-64\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[64]</a>穆斯林太监被派遣为帖木儿大使。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-65\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[65]</a>张夫派遣阮氏，阮安，范红，陈武，王进等越南太监到明朝。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-CommitteeGoodrich1976_2-66\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[66]</a>在明朝与朝鲜的早期争执期间，当争夺对满洲的女真人的影响之争时，韩国官员甚至在未满足他们要求的情况下被出生于朝鲜的明太监大使所困。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Wang-67\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[67]</a>有些大使自高自大，例如辛国生（Sin Kwi-saeng），1398年，他在国王面前的晚宴上喝醉酒并挥舞着小刀。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-68\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[68]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-TwitchettMote1998-69\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[69]</a>后来中韩关系变得和，可亲，朝鲜朝臣在明朝朝廷的座位安排始终是朝贡中最高的。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Wang-67\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[67]</a>&nbsp;1435年后，韩国停止向人类致敬。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Wang-67\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[67]</a>韩国总共派出198位太监到明朝。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-70\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[70]</a>明代太监帽与韩国王室帽相似，表明明代太监帽的国外渊源，其中许多来自东南亚和韩国。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-71\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[71]</a><br>\n<br>\n在<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miao_Rebellions_(Ming_dynasty)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">苗族起义期间</a>，明朝总督在部落叛乱时rated弃了数千名<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miao_people\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">苗族</a>男孩，然后将其作为奴隶给各种官员。明朝天皇得知此事后，命苗的总督受到明天顺皇帝的谴责和谴责。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Tsai1996-59\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[59]</a>：16<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zhu_Shuang\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">朱爽</a>（秦亲王）虽然毒品很高，但在与少数藏族人民的战争之后，一些some子被cast割，藏族妇女被查封，因此，他因服药过量死亡而受到谴责。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-72\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[72]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-73\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[73]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-74\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[74]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-75\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[75]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-76\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[76]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-77\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[77]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-78\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[78]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-79\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[79]</a><br>\n<br>\n1406年1月30日，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ryukyu_Kingdom\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">琉球</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yongle_Emperor\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">皇帝</a>对<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ryukyu_Kingdom\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">琉元首cast</a>割了一些自己的孩子成为太监以将其交给皇帝时表示了恐惧。永乐皇帝说，那些被rated割的男孩是无辜的，不应该被cast割，他将男孩归还给琉球，并指示他们不要再送太监。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-80\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[80]</a><br>\n<br>\n反猪宰杀法令导致人们猜测，正德皇帝采用伊斯兰教，原因是他使用了穆斯林太监，后者委托生产波斯和阿拉伯文的白色和蓝色瓷器。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Levenson(U.S.)1991-81\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[81]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-O&#39;Kane2012-82\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[82]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-83\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[83]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-84\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[84]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Publishing2010-85\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[85]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Kuiper2010_2-86\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[86]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Publishing2010_2-87\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[87]&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Valenstein1988-88\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[88]</a>穆斯林太监在1496年为修复牛街清真寺捐款。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Naquin2000-89\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[89]</a>究竟谁是反猪屠宰法令的幕后黑手，这一点还不得而知。<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eunuch#cite_note-Haar2006-90\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">[90]</a>","date":"2019-12-13","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}